query:
SELECT r.startTime, COUNT(*) as cnt, GROUP_CONCAT(r.id ORDER BY r.id) as ids
FROM ridingRecords r
INNER JOIN users u ON r.userId = u.id
WHERE u.name = '로버'
GROUP BY r.startTime
HAVING COUNT(*) > 1
ORDER BY cnt DESC;
